### ==========================================
### 系统集成 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token（管理员）
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：获取集成配置
GET http://localhost:18081/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：保存集成配置
PUT http://localhost:18081/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "integrationConfig": {
    "wecomCorpId": "ww_test",
    "wecomAgentId": "1000001",
    "wecomSecret": "test_secret",
    "orgEnabled": false
  }
}

### 3. 正常流程：审计日志列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/audit?page=0&size=10&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 正常流程：审计日志搜索
GET http://localhost:18081/api/audit?keyword=登录&page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 正常流程：审计日志按模块筛选
GET http://localhost:18081/api/audit?module=PROJECT&page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 正常流程：个人操作日志
GET http://localhost:18081/api/audit/my?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 边界：非 auditor 访问审计日志
# @name staffLogin
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "xiaowang",
  "password": "123456"
}

@staffToken = {{staffLogin.response.body.data.token}}

GET http://localhost:18081/api/audit?page=0&size=1
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

### 8. 正常流程：通知列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/notifications?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 正常流程：未读通知数
GET http://localhost:18081/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. 边界：空审计日志日期范围
GET http://localhost:18081/api/audit?startDate=2099-01-01&endDate=2099-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
